{"tid":2444941,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"打鼓嶺警車私家車相撞 4警員送院","createTime":"2021-03-13T08:29:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T14:31:06.000Z","uid":240362,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6faa1c711526d06701f36d2fb3fb52f492689c6f","tid":2444941,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T08:29:26.000Z","msg":"2021-03-13 16:16<br />\n打鼓嶺坪輋路中午發生交通意外，一輛私家車與一輛警車相撞。事件中共有5人受傷，包括4名警員。<br />\n<br />\n事發在中午12時23分，一輛警車沿坪輋路往沙頭角公路方向行駛，當駛至打鼓嶺坪輋路時，一輛私家車從一停車場駛出至坪輋路，兩車其後相撞。事發後，警車及私家車的車頭位置均有損毀。在涉事警車上，負責駕駛的男警務人員腰部受傷，車上另外3名男警務人員輕傷，至於39歲李姓私家車司機則腿部受傷。受傷的5人清醒，被送往北區醫院治理。"},{"pid":"d576f162ba59bfad7e7cc65d30383e1a50f9b54c","tid":2444941,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T08:29:50.000Z","msg":"開心"},{"pid":"65c41ff1af572fb48051776aefc81b8832ed3d8a","tid":2444941,"uid":387826,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T08:29:52.000Z","msg":"中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a452fc153f9ec45319c3bc4b7f15c26cabaf6b2","tid":2444941,"uid":15697,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T08:30:05.000Z","msg":"會唔會用国安法拉個司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89004d6858b2805470f1b34727d34f7e2059c3db","tid":2444941,"uid":44209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T08:31:27.000Z","msg":"私家車襲警？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e4c9235339de4db59e59d161df832a78c68ec7","tid":2444941,"uid":3457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T08:31:42.000Z","msg":"私家車司機係味要國安處跟進？"},{"pid":"0496892178f2f16de5d11a432ce931873abdef94","tid":2444941,"uid":80564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T08:32:12.000Z","msg":"私家車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7d1783f648087892b986e4f692091b73f497e0","tid":2444941,"uid":86509,"like":0,"d